quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  92,15,"Shalikwinjilamwo tawe halali Omubii muno!"
  92,16,"Ulia wakatsula mana nafutara omukongo."
  92,17,"Ne ulia waria Nyasaye alireebwa ehale ninakwo."
  92,18,"Ulia urusinjia omwandu kukwe khulwa okhwitswenula."
  92,19,"Ne shikali mbu aliho yesiyesi wamukholela amalayi lano khamurunje tawe."
  92,20,"Halali nokhukhaaba obweni bwa Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi, Oweekulu muno."
  92,21,"Naye yakhachame!"
  93,1,"Nditsuba khu isenya (okhurula itsuli okhula eshitere)!"
  93,2,"Nditsuba khushilo olwa shinjilanga!"
  93,3,"Nyasaye wuwo shiyakhulekha tawe, nohomba shiyakhusinyishila tawe."
  93,4,"Ne obulamu bwomwikulu nobulayi khwiwe okhushira bwa khushialo."
  93,5,"Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi alakhuwa okhula ochame."
  93,6,"Shiyakhunyoola noli omufwilwa mana nakhuwa eshimenyo?"
  93,7,"Ne nakhunyoola niwakora, mana nakhulunjisia?"
  93,8,"Ne nakhunyoola noli omumanani mana nakhuyindiasia?"
  93,9,"Kho omwana omufwilwa, olamufuolafia tawe!"
  93,10,"Naye usaba olamuwusa tawe!"
  93,11,"Ne obwokholo bwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi obuboole."
  94,1,"Shikhwakhubambulila eshilifu shishio tawe?"
  94,2,"Ne nikhukhuruula omusiko kukwo?"
  94,3,"Kwali nikwafunaka omukongo kukwo?"
  94,4,"Ne nikhura hekulu okhurumbulwa khukhwo?"
  94,5,"Ne toto halala nende obusiro buliho obwangu."
  94,6,"Toto halala nende obusiro buliho obwangu."
  94,7,"Kho, nonyoola obwiyangu, khola eshinani."
  94,8,"Ne yenya muno ewa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi."